    lol:spellTooltip "Akali drops a smoke bomb, unleashing a spreading cover of smoke lasting {{ baseduration }} seconds and granting herself {{ movementspeed }}% Move Speed decaying over {{ movementspeedduration }} seconds.Akali increases her max Energy by {{ energyrestore }} while the shroud is active. While inside the smoke, Akali is Invisible.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
