champ:Akshan a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Akshan" ;
    lol:championKey "166" ;
    lol:championName "Akshan" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Rogue Sentinel" ;
    lol:blurb "Raising an eyebrow in the face of danger, Akshan fights evil with dashing charisma, righteous vengeance, and a conspicuous lack of shirts. He is highly skilled in the art of stealth combat, able to evade the eyes of his enemies and reappear when they..." ;
    lol:lore "Raising an eyebrow in the face of danger, Akshan fights evil with dashing charisma, righteous vengeance, and a conspicuous lack of shirts. He is highly skilled in the art of stealth combat, able to evade the eyes of his enemies and reappear when they least expect him. With a keen sense of justice and a legendary death-reversing weapon, he rights the wrongs of Runeterra's many scoundrels while living by his own moral code: “Don't be an ass.”" ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.01" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Raising an eyebrow in the face of danger, Akshan fights evil with dashing charisma, righteous vengeance, and a conspicuous lack of shirts. He is highly skilled in the art of stealth combat, able to evade the eyes of his enemies and reappear when they least expect him. With a keen sense of justice and a legendary death-reversing weapon, he rights the wrongs of Runeterra's many scoundrels while living by his own moral code: “Don't be an ass.”" ;
