champ:Alistar a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Alistar" ;
    lol:championKey "12" ;
    lol:championName "Alistar" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Minotaur" ;
    lol:blurb "Always a mighty warrior with a fearsome reputation, Alistar seeks revenge for the death of his clan at the hands of the Noxian empire. Though he was enslaved and forced into the life of a gladiator, his unbreakable will was what kept him from truly..." ;
    lol:lore "Always a mighty warrior with a fearsome reputation, Alistar seeks revenge for the death of his clan at the hands of the Noxian empire. Though he was enslaved and forced into the life of a gladiator, his unbreakable will was what kept him from truly becoming a beast. Now, free of the chains of his former masters, he fights in the name of the downtrodden and the disadvantaged, his rage as much a weapon as his horns, hooves and fists." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.15" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Using Pulverize can allow you to establish better positioning for Headbutt." ;
    lol:allyTip "Move Speed is very important on Alistar. Consider which boots to buy carefully." ;
    lol:allyTip "Using Flash can allow you catch your target off guard to knock them back into your allies with Pulverize and Headbutt." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Alistar is very disruptive but very tough - try to target more fragile damage dealers." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Watch out for the Pulverize-Headbutt combo when around turrets." ;
    lol:enemyTip "When Alistar uses his ultimate, it's often better to move back and wait until the effect wears off before attacking him." ;
