    lol:spellDescription "Ambessa whips her twin drakehounds around herself, damaging and slowing nearby enemies. Initiating Drakehound's Step from this ability causes her to strike a second time at the end of its dash." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Ambessa whips her chains around, dealing {{ calc_damage_flat }} physical damage and Slowing enemies by {{ slow_amount*100 }}%, which decays over {{ slow_duration }} second. Initiating Drakehound's Step from this Ability will trigger an additional strike.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
