    lol:spellDescription "Bel'Veth slams her tail to the ground, damaging, knocking up, and slowing her enemies." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Bel'Veth slams her tail, dealing {{ damage }} magic damage, Knocking Up foes for {{ duration }} seconds, and Slowing them by {{ slowpercent*100 }}% for {{ slowduration }} seconds. If a champion is hit, this refreshes the Cooldown of Void Surge in that direction.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
