spell:Braum_Passive a lol:PassiveAbility, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:spellName "Concussive Blows" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Braum's basic attacks apply Concussive Blows. Once the first stack is applied, ally basic attacks also stack Concussive Blows. Upon reaching 4 stacks, the target is stunned and takes magic damage. For the next few seconds they cannot receive new stacks, but take bonus magic damage from Braum's attacks." ;
    lol:belongsToChampion champ:Braum .

