champ:Caitlyn a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Caitlyn" ;
    lol:championKey "51" ;
    lol:championName "Caitlyn" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Sheriff of Piltover" ;
    lol:blurb "Renowned as its finest peacekeeper, Caitlyn Kiramman is also Piltover's best shot at ridding the city of its elusive criminal elements. She is often paired with Vi, acting as a cool counterpoint to her partner's more impetuous nature. Even though she..." ;
    lol:lore "Renowned as its finest peacekeeper, Caitlyn Kiramman is also Piltover's best shot at ridding the city of its elusive criminal elements. She is often paired with Vi, acting as a cool counterpoint to her partner's more impetuous nature. Even though she carries a one-of-a-kind hextech rifle, Caitlyn's most powerful weapon is her superior intellect, allowing her to lay elaborate traps for any lawbreakers foolish enough to operate in the City of Progress." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.01" ;
    lol:costBE "225"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "260"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Make use of her Yordle Snap Traps by placing them pre-emptively to ensure that you'll have one off of cooldown during combat." ;
    lol:allyTip "Avoid using Ace in the Hole in large team melees as it might be blocked by the wrong target." ;
    lol:allyTip "Fire 90 Caliber Net away from the opponent to close the gap or hop over walls." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Keep behind allied minions if Caitlyn is harassing you with Piltover Peacemaker (it deals less damage with each subsequent target)." ;
    lol:enemyTip "You can intercept Ace in the Hole's missile from hitting an ally if you stand in its path." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Marksman ;
    lol:hasResourceType res:Mana ;
