    lol:spellDescription "Devours an enemy unit, dealing a high amount of true damage. If the target is killed, Cho'Gath grows, gaining maximum Health." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Cho'Gath ravenously feeds on an enemy, dealing {{ rdamage }} true damage to champions or {{ rmonsterdamage }} to minions or jungle monsters. If this kills the target, Cho'Gath gains a stack, which causes him to grow in size and gain {{ rhealthperstack }} max Health. Only {{ rminionmaxstacks }} stacks can be gained from minions and non-epic jungle monsters. {{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
    lol:maxRank "3"^^xsd:integer ;
