    lol:spellTooltip "Corki fires a missile that explodes on the first enemy hit, dealing {{ rsmallmissiledamage }} physical damage to surrounding enemies. Every third missile instead deals {{ rbigmissiledamage }} physical damage.This Ability has up to {{ maxammotooltip }} charges. Basic attacks against champions reduce the time between charges by {{ attackrefund }} seconds on hit.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
