champ:Ezreal a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Ezreal" ;
    lol:championKey "81" ;
    lol:championName "Ezreal" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Prodigal Explorer" ;
    lol:blurb "A dashing adventurer, unknowingly gifted in the magical arts, Ezreal raids long-lost catacombs, tangles with ancient curses, and overcomes seemingly impossible odds with ease. His courage and bravado knowing no bounds, he prefers to improvise his way..." ;
    lol:lore "A dashing adventurer, unknowingly gifted in the magical arts, Ezreal raids long-lost catacombs, tangles with ancient curses, and overcomes seemingly impossible odds with ease. His courage and bravado knowing no bounds, he prefers to improvise his way out of any situation, relying partially on his wits, but mostly on his mystical Shuriman gauntlet, which he uses to unleash devastating arcane blasts. One thing is for sure—whenever Ezreal is around, trouble isn't too far behind. Or ahead. Probably everywhere." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.03" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Use Arcane Shift to help line up your other skill shots." ;
    lol:allyTip "You can play Ezreal either as a Attack Damage carry or Ability Power carry depending on how you build him." ;
    lol:allyTip "You can line up Trueshot Barrage to hit multiple minion waves or even Monsters." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Ezreal is a very fragile champion so take the fight to him." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Ezreal is completely skill shot based, so make sure to keep minions in between you." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Mystic Shot applies on-hit effects including the Crest of Cinders." ;
