    lol:spellDescription "Fiddlesticks slashes an area with its scythe, slowing all enemies hit and silencing enemies hit in the center of the slash." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Fiddlesticks unleashes dark magic, dealing {{ damage }} magic damage and Slowing by {{ slowamount*-100 }}% for {{ silenceduration }} seconds. Enemies in the center are also Silenced for the duration.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
