champ:Fiora a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Fiora" ;
    lol:championKey "114" ;
    lol:championName "Fiora" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Grand Duelist" ;
    lol:blurb "The most feared duelist in all Valoran, Fiora is as renowned for her brusque manner and cunning mind as she is for the speed of her bluesteel rapier. Born to House Laurent in the kingdom of Demacia, Fiora took control of the family from her father in..." ;
    lol:lore "The most feared duelist in all Valoran, Fiora is as renowned for her brusque manner and cunning mind as she is for the speed of her bluesteel rapier. Born to House Laurent in the kingdom of Demacia, Fiora took control of the family from her father in the wake of a scandal that nearly destroyed them. House Laurent's reputation was sundered, but Fiora bends her every effort to restore her family's honor and return them to their rightful place among the great and good of Demacia." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.16" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Thanks to Duelist's Dance, Fiora excels at quick trades. Use the Move Speed boost from striking a Vital to escape unscathed or set up for the next one." ;
    lol:allyTip "Grand Challenge allows Fiora to take down even the most durable opponents and then recover if successful, so do not hesitate to attack the enemy's front line." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Duelist's Dance shows you where Fiora will try to attack from, so be ready to punish her when she tries." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Be careful when casting immobilizing disables on Fiora. If her Riposte is available, she can turn their power against you." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Fighter ;
    lol:hasRole role:Assassin ;
    lol:hasResourceType res:Mana ;
    lol:isFromRegion region:Demacia ;
    lol:playsPosition pos:Top ;
