    lol:spellDescription "Galio will briefly step back and charge, knocking up the first enemy champion he encounters." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Galio lunges forward with a mighty blow, Knocking Up for {{ knockupduration }} seconds and dealing {{ totaldamage }} magic damage to the first champion hit. Other enemies in the way take {{ pvedamage }} magic damage.Galio's dash stops on hitting terrain.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
