champ:Garen a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Garen" ;
    lol:championKey "86" ;
    lol:championName "Garen" ;
    lol:championTitle "The Might of Demacia" ;
    lol:blurb "A proud and noble warrior, Garen fights as one of the Dauntless Vanguard. He is popular among his fellows, and respected well enough by his enemies—not least as a scion of the prestigious Crownguard family, entrusted with defending Demacia and its..." ;
    lol:lore "A proud and noble warrior, Garen fights as one of the Dauntless Vanguard. He is popular among his fellows, and respected well enough by his enemies—not least as a scion of the prestigious Crownguard family, entrusted with defending Demacia and its ideals. Clad in magic-resistant armor and bearing a mighty broadsword, Garen stands ready to confront mages and sorcerers on the field of battle, in a veritable whirlwind of righteous steel." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.05" ;
    lol:costBE "225"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "260"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Garen's regeneration greatly increases if he can avoid receiving damage for several seconds." ;
    lol:allyTip "Judgment deals maximum damage when only hitting a single target. For effective trading, try to position such that only the enemy champion is hit." ;
    lol:allyTip "Garen is only constrained by cooldowns, making items such as Black Cleaver very effective for him." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Stack armor items to lower the large amount of physical damage that Garen deals out." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Try to run away from Garen as your health gets lower, as he can execute you quickly with Demacian Justice." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Be careful about attacking Garen in brush. It often will lead to taking full damage from Judgment." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Judgment deals maximum damage when only hitting a single target. If getting out of its radius isn't possible, move through allied minions to reduce damage taken." ;
