champ:Graves a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Graves" ;
    lol:championKey "104" ;
    lol:championName "Graves" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Outlaw" ;
    lol:blurb "Malcolm Graves is a renowned mercenary, gambler, and thief—a wanted man in every city and empire he has visited. Even though he has an explosive temper, he possesses a strict sense of criminal honor, often enforced at the business end of his..." ;
    lol:lore "Malcolm Graves is a renowned mercenary, gambler, and thief—a wanted man in every city and empire he has visited. Even though he has an explosive temper, he possesses a strict sense of criminal honor, often enforced at the business end of his double-barreled shotgun Destiny. In recent years, he has reconciled a troubled partnership with Twisted Fate, and together they have prospered once more in the turmoil of Bilgewater's criminal underbelly." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.04" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Smoke Screen can be used both to escape and to set up a kill." ;
    lol:allyTip "Using Quickdraw to get into range and delivering a point blank Buckshot can do lots of damage." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Graves deals mostly physical damage so Armor is an effective counter." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Leaving the Smoke Screen's area of effect removes the harmful effect immediately." ;
