    lol:spellTooltip "Graves fires a powder round dealing {{ totaldamage }} physical damage. After 1 second or after colliding with terrain, it detonates, dealing {{ totaldetonationdamage }} physical damage along the travel path again and to enemies near the blast.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
