    lol:spellTooltip "Hecarim cleaves nearby enemies for {{ damage }} physical damage. If this Ability hits, he gains a stack that decreases its Cooldown by {{ rampagecooldownreduction }} seconds and increases its damage by {{ rampagebonusdamageperc }}% for {{ e6 }} seconds. Stacks up to {{ e2 }} times.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
