    lol:spellDescription "Hammer Stance: Passive: Restores Mana per strike. Active: Creates a field of lightning damaging nearby enemies for several seconds.Cannon Stance: Gains a burst of energy, increasing Attack Speed to maximum for several attacks." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Mercury Hammer - Passive: Jayce's Hammer Attacks grant {{ spell.jaycestaticfield:managain }} Mana.Mercury Hammer - Active: Jayce creates an electric aura dealing {{ spell.jaycestaticfield:damage }} magic damage over {{ spell.jaycestaticfield:duration }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
