champ:Kai_Sa a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Kaisa" ;
    lol:championKey "145" ;
    lol:championName "Kai'Sa" ;
    lol:championTitle "Daughter of the Void" ;
    lol:blurb "Claimed by the Void when she was only a child, Kai'Sa managed to survive through sheer tenacity and strength of will. Her experiences have made her a deadly hunter and, to some, the harbinger of a future they would rather not live to see. Having entered..." ;
    lol:lore "Claimed by the Void when she was only a child, Kai'Sa managed to survive through sheer tenacity and strength of will. Her experiences have made her a deadly hunter and, to some, the harbinger of a future they would rather not live to see. Having entered into an uneasy symbiosis with a living Void carapace, the time will soon come when she must decide whether to forgive those mortals who would call her a monster, and defeat the coming darkness together… or simply to forget, as the Void consumes the world that left her behind." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.23" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Try to catch enemy carries alone to burst them with Icathian Rain." ;
    lol:allyTip "Work with your teammates to set up your Ultimate and optimize damage with your passive." ;
    lol:allyTip "Make sure to buy items that will evolve at least 1 or 2 of your spells." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Kai'Sa is very good at picking off isolated enemies. Stick together against her." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Kai'Sa is very vulnerable to getting outranged by mages and long range carries." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Make sure to place wards in your blind spots so you can see Kai'Sa coming." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Marksman ;
    lol:hasRole role:Mage ;
