    lol:spellDescription "Kai'Sa briefly increases her Move Speed, then increases her Attack Speed.Living Weapon: Supercharge is upgraded to briefly grant Invisibility." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Kai'Sa supercharges her void energy, gaining {{ totalmovespeed }} Move Speed and becoming Ghosted while charging, then gaining {{ e5 }}% Attack Speed for {{ e2 }} seconds.Attacks reduce this Ability's Cooldown by {{ e4 }} seconds.Evolved: Kai'Sa also becomes Invisible for {{ e7 }} seconds.Current: {{ f10.1 }}%/{{ e6 }}% Bonus Attack Speed{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
