champ:Karthus a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Karthus" ;
    lol:championKey "30" ;
    lol:championName "Karthus" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Deathsinger" ;
    lol:blurb "The harbinger of oblivion, Karthus is an undying spirit whose haunting songs are a prelude to the horror of his nightmarish appearance. The living fear the eternity of undeath, but Karthus sees only beauty and purity in its embrace, a perfect union of..." ;
    lol:lore "The harbinger of oblivion, Karthus is an undying spirit whose haunting songs are a prelude to the horror of his nightmarish appearance. The living fear the eternity of undeath, but Karthus sees only beauty and purity in its embrace, a perfect union of life and death. When Karthus emerges from the Shadow Isles, it is to bring the joy of death to mortals, an apostle of the unliving." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.03" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Ask your allies to help point out when you should use Requiem to get kills in different lanes." ;
    lol:allyTip "Lay Waste is very strong at farming minions and harassing enemy champions." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Karthus can cast spells for a short duration after he is killed. Move away from his corpse to be safe." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Make sure you always have enough health to survive Requiem, even if you have to go back to the base more frequently to heal." ;
