champ:Kassadin a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Kassadin" ;
    lol:championKey "38" ;
    lol:championName "Kassadin" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Void Walker" ;
    lol:blurb "Cutting a burning swath through the darkest places of the world, Kassadin knows his days are numbered. A widely traveled Shuriman guide and adventurer, he had chosen to raise a family among the peaceful southern tribes—until the day his village was..." ;
    lol:lore "Cutting a burning swath through the darkest places of the world, Kassadin knows his days are numbered. A widely traveled Shuriman guide and adventurer, he had chosen to raise a family among the peaceful southern tribes—until the day his village was consumed by the Void. He vowed vengeance, combining a number of arcane artifacts and forbidden technologies for the struggle ahead. Finally, Kassadin set out for the wastelands of Icathia, ready to face any monstrous Void-construct in his search for their self-proclaimed prophet, Malzahar." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.04" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Kassadin has multiple item paths; he can go caster via Mana and Ability Power or anti-caster with Cooldown Reduction and Magic Resist." ;
    lol:allyTip "Kassadin's ultimate has many uses and is on a shorter cooldown than most, use it often." ;
    lol:allyTip "Try to get the Ancient Golem buff to counteract Riftwalk's increasing Mana cost." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Kassadin deals mostly magic damage. If he's doing well consider buying magic resist items like Mercury's Treads and Banshee's Veil." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Each time Kassadin consecutively uses Riftwalk, he pays more and more mana. Keep this in mind as you chase him." ;
    lol:enemyTip "It takes 6 spell casts for Kassadin's slow, Force Pulse, to become castable. If he levels up that ability, judiciously use your own skills while laning against him." ;
