    lol:spellDescription "Kassadin teleports to a nearby location dealing damage to nearby enemy units. Multiple Riftwalks in a short period of time cost additional Mana but also deal additional damage." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Kassadin teleports to a nearby location, dealing {{ basedamage }} magic damage.Each subsequent use of this Ability within the next {{ rstackduration }} seconds doubles the Mana cost and deals an additional {{ bonusdamage }} magic damage. The cost and damage increases can stack up to {{ maxstacks }} times.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
