champ:Katarina a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Katarina" ;
    lol:championKey "55" ;
    lol:championName "Katarina" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Sinister Blade" ;
    lol:blurb "Decisive in judgment and lethal in combat, Katarina is a Noxian assassin of the highest caliber. Eldest daughter to the legendary General Du Couteau, she made her talents known with swift kills against unsuspecting enemies. Her fiery ambition has driven..." ;
    lol:lore "Decisive in judgment and lethal in combat, Katarina is a Noxian assassin of the highest caliber. Eldest daughter to the legendary General Du Couteau, she made her talents known with swift kills against unsuspecting enemies. Her fiery ambition has driven her to pursue heavily-guarded targets, even at the risk of endangering her allies—but no matter the mission, Katarina will not hesitate to execute her duty amid a whirlwind of serrated daggers." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.03" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Picking up Daggers will significantly reduce Shunpo's cooldown." ;
    lol:allyTip "Try waiting until the other team is distracted with fighting your team, and use Shunpo to teleport into the fray and unleash a devastating Death Lotus." ;
    lol:allyTip "Using Shunpo on an allied Champion, Dagger, or minion can be a great escape tactic." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Katarina's abilities deal magic damage, so even if she's building Attack Damage items, get magic resistance to counter her." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Try to save a disable for when Katarina uses her Death Lotus." ;
