champ:Kayn a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Kayn" ;
    lol:championKey "141" ;
    lol:championName "Kayn" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Shadow Reaper" ;
    lol:blurb "A peerless practitioner of lethal shadow magic, Shieda Kayn battles to achieve his true destiny—to one day lead the Order of Shadow into a new era of Ionian supremacy. He wields the sentient darkin weapon Rhaast, undeterred by its creeping corruption of..." ;
    lol:lore "A peerless practitioner of lethal shadow magic, Shieda Kayn battles to achieve his true destiny—to one day lead the Order of Shadow into a new era of Ionian supremacy. He wields the sentient darkin weapon Rhaast, undeterred by its creeping corruption of his body and mind. There are only two possible outcomes: either Kayn bends the weapon to his will... or the malevolent blade consumes him completely, paving the way for the destruction of all Runeterra." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.03" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Look at the line-up of both your team and the enemy's team when picking your form." ;
    lol:allyTip "Remember that nearby enemies can see which wall you're in." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Umbral Trespass requires Kayn to damage a target first. Try to dodge Blade's Reach to deny him a long range cast of Umbral Trespass." ;
    lol:enemyTip "When Kayn is in terrain near you, you will get a visual warning on the edge of the terrain he's in." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Damage Kayn while he's in Shadow Step to shorten its duration, or apply hard crowd control (stun, charm, knockup, etc) to end Shadow Step immediately." ;
