    lol:spellTooltip "Kayn gains {{ e1 }}% Move Speed, becomes Ghosted, and can move through Terrain for {{ e2 }} seconds. When he first enters terrain, he restores {{ totalhealing }} Health.Being Immobilized and spending more than {{ e3 }} consecutive seconds outside of Terrain ends this Ability early.Shadow Assassin: Gain {{ e5 }}% Move Speed, Slow immunity, and reduce the Cooldown to {{ assassincdreduction }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
