    lol:spellDescription "Kennen passively deals extra damage and adds a Mark of the Storm to his target every few attacks, and he can activate this ability to damage and add another Mark of the Storm to targets who are already marked." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Passive: Every 5th Attack deals an additional {{ totaldamagepassive }} magic damage.Active: Kennen sends out a blast of electricity, dealing {{ totaldamageactive }} magic damage to nearby enemies affected by Mark of the Storm.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
