champ:Kog_Maw a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "KogMaw" ;
    lol:championKey "96" ;
    lol:championName "Kog'Maw" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Mouth of the Abyss" ;
    lol:blurb "Belched forth from a rotting Void incursion deep in the wastelands of Icathia, Kog'Maw is an inquisitive yet putrid creature with a caustic, gaping mouth. This particular Void-spawn needs to gnaw and drool on anything within reach to truly understand it..." ;
    lol:lore "Belched forth from a rotting Void incursion deep in the wastelands of Icathia, Kog'Maw is an inquisitive yet putrid creature with a caustic, gaping mouth. This particular Void-spawn needs to gnaw and drool on anything within reach to truly understand it. Though not inherently evil, Kog'Maw's beguiling naiveté is dangerous, as it often precedes a feeding frenzy—not for sustenance, but to satisfy its unending curiosity." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.21" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Kog'Maw can outrange most champions with his Bio-Arcane Barrage ability." ;
    lol:allyTip "Use Void Ooze to set up a perfect Living Artillery." ;
    lol:allyTip "Make the most out of your Icathian Surprise." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Kog'Maw doesn't have a good escape ability, so he is especially prone to ganks." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Run away from Kog'Maw after he dies!!!!" ;
    lol:enemyTip "The range on Living Artillery increases each rank." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Bio-Arcane Barrage allows Kog'Maw to kill Baron Nashor extremely early. It can be valuable to ward Nashor when Kog'Maw completes his Blade of the Ruined King." ;
