    lol:spellTooltip "When used on an ally, Lulu grants {{ totalms }} Move Speed and {{ e7 }}% Attack Speed for {{ e5 }} seconds.When used on an enemy, Lulu Polymorphs them for {{ e3 }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
