    lol:spellDescription "If cast on an ally, commands Pix to jump to an ally and shield them. He then follows them and aids their attacks. If cast on an enemy, commands Pix to jump to an enemy and damage them. He then follows them and grants you vision of that enemy." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "When used on an ally, Pix jumps to them and grants Pix, Faerie Companion for {{ e1 }} seconds. If the ally is a champion, Pix also grants {{ totalshield }} Shield for {{ e7 }} seconds.When used on an enemy champion, Pix hampers them, dealing {{ totaldamage }} magic damage and granting True Sight of them for {{ e6 }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
