    lol:spellDescription "Fires an anomaly of twisted light to an area, which slows nearby enemies. Lux can detonate it to damage enemies in the area of effect." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Lux creates a light zone that Slows by {{ e1 }}% and reveals the area. After {{ e3 }} seconds or on Recasting this Ability, it detonates, dealing {{ totaldamagett }} magic damage and Slowing for an additional {{ slowlingerduration }} second.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
