champ:Morgana a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Morgana" ;
    lol:championKey "25" ;
    lol:championName "Morgana" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Fallen" ;
    lol:blurb "Conflicted between her celestial and mortal natures, Morgana bound her wings to embrace humanity, and inflicts her pain and bitterness upon the dishonest and the corrupt. She rejects laws and traditions she believes are unjust, and fights for truth from..." ;
    lol:lore "Conflicted between her celestial and mortal natures, Morgana bound her wings to embrace humanity, and inflicts her pain and bitterness upon the dishonest and the corrupt. She rejects laws and traditions she believes are unjust, and fights for truth from the shadows of Demacia—even as others seek to repress it—by casting shields and chains of dark fire. More than anything else, Morgana truly believes that even the banished and outcast may one day rise again." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.21" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Shrewd use of Black Shield can determine the outcome of team fights." ;
    lol:allyTip "Items that provide survivability allow Morgana to become extremely difficult to kill in conjunction with Black Shield and Soul Shackles." ;
    lol:allyTip "Tormented Shadow is an excellent farming tool if you're by yourself in a lane." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Tormented Shadow deals tons of damage to units missing large amounts of Health. When low on Health, be wary of Morgana's attempts to trap you within its reach." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Morgana often needs to land Dark Binding to setup her other attacks. Use your minions as shields against Dark Binding." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Black Shield makes Morgana immune to disabling effects, but can be broken with magic damage." ;
