champ:Nasus a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Nasus" ;
    lol:championKey "75" ;
    lol:championName "Nasus" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Curator of the Sands" ;
    lol:blurb "Nasus is an imposing, jackal-headed Ascended being from ancient Shurima, a heroic figure regarded as a demigod by the people of the desert. Fiercely intelligent, he was a guardian of knowledge and peerless strategist whose wisdom guided the ancient..." ;
    lol:lore "Nasus is an imposing, jackal-headed Ascended being from ancient Shurima, a heroic figure regarded as a demigod by the people of the desert. Fiercely intelligent, he was a guardian of knowledge and peerless strategist whose wisdom guided the ancient empire of Shurima to greatness for many centuries. After the fall of the empire, he went into self-imposed exile, becoming little more than a legend. Now that the ancient city of Shurima has risen once more, he has returned, determined to ensure it never falls again." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.24" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Paying attention to last hitting with Siphoning Strike will have a large impact at the end of a game." ;
    lol:allyTip "If you're solo, Spirit Fire is a great way to farm a lane. It can be bad if you're in a lane with 2 and you push too far. Find the right balance between Siphoning Strike last hits and AoE farming." ;
    lol:allyTip "If you have low defenses, people will focus you down even during your ultimate. Try buying some survivability items even in your DPS builds." ;
    lol:enemyTip "While transformed by his ultimate, Nasus is stronger than most champions in the League. Engage him only if you have a clear advantage." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Max rank Wither is a very effective counter to Attack Damage characters, so try to avoid getting caught alone by it." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Nasus is prone to being kited. Try not to engage him at full Health." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Fighter ;
    lol:hasRole role:Tank ;
