    lol:championKey "518" ;
    lol:championName "Neeko" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Curious Chameleon" ;
    lol:blurb "Hailing from a long lost tribe of vastaya, Neeko can blend into any crowd by borrowing the appearances of others, even absorbing something of their emotional state to tell friend from foe in an instant. No one is ever sure where—or who—Neeko might be..." ;
    lol:lore "Hailing from a long lost tribe of vastaya, Neeko can blend into any crowd by borrowing the appearances of others, even absorbing something of their emotional state to tell friend from foe in an instant. No one is ever sure where—or who—Neeko might be, but those who intend to do her harm will soon witness her true colors revealed, and feel the full power of her primordial spirit magic unleashed upon them." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.05" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "You can set her passive to use hotkeys in the options menu. The default is Shift+F1~F5" ;
    lol:allyTip "Try to use Inherent Glamour sparingly, ineffective uses will put enemies on the alert." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Standing behind minions against Neeko is very dangerous as Tangle-Barbs become stronger." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Pop Blossom's warning visuals are invisible if Neeko is disguised." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Mage ;
    lol:hasRole role:Support ;
