    lol:spellDescription "Pantheon dashes to a target, damaging and stunning them." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Pantheon leaps on his target, Stunning for {{ stunduration }} second and dealing {{ maxhealthdamagecalc }} max Health physical damage.Mortal Will Bonus: Pantheon's next Attack strikes {{ empowerednumhits }} times, dealing a total of {{ empowereddamagemultcalcmodified }} physical damage.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
