champ:Pyke a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Pyke" ;
    lol:championKey "555" ;
    lol:championName "Pyke" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Bloodharbor Ripper" ;
    lol:blurb "A renowned harpooner from the slaughter docks of Bilgewater, Pyke should have met his death in the belly of a gigantic jaull-fish… and yet, he returned. Now, stalking the dank alleys and backways of his former hometown, he uses his new supernatural..." ;
    lol:lore "A renowned harpooner from the slaughter docks of Bilgewater, Pyke should have met his death in the belly of a gigantic jaull-fish… and yet, he returned. Now, stalking the dank alleys and backways of his former hometown, he uses his new supernatural gifts to bring a swift and gruesome end to those who make their fortune by exploiting others—and a city that prides itself on hunting monsters now finds a monster hunting them." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.10" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Pyke is very fragile so don't be afraid to temporarily run from a fight. You can regenerate a significant amount of health from Gift of the Drowned Ones when enemies can't see you." ;
    lol:allyTip "Hitting an enemy with the Hold version of Bone Skewer will always pull them the same distance. Use it in melee range to throw targets behind you." ;
    lol:allyTip "The Tap version of Bone Skewer is much faster and deals additional damage." ;
    lol:allyTip "A lot of your agressive spells are also your escapes. Make sure you always have a plan to get out of the fight." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Pyke regenerates a significant amount of damage he has taken from enemy champions, but only when you can't see him!" ;
    lol:enemyTip "When Pyke is hidden nearby in his Ghostwater Dive, sharks will circle underneath your feet." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Try not to stand near low health allies. If Pyke executes them using Death From Below, you might be next on the list." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Support ;
    lol:hasRole role:Assassin ;
    lol:hasResourceType res:Mana ;
    lol:isFromRegion region:Bilgewater ;
    lol:playsPosition pos:Support ;
