    lol:spellDescription "Quinn calls Valor to mark an enemy and hinder its vision before damaging all enemies in the immediate area." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Quinn orders Valor to dive, making the first enemy hit Vulnerable, reducing their vision radius for {{ e3 }} seconds and dealing {{ totaldamage }} physical damage to all surrounding enemies.If the first enemy struck is not a champion, it is Disarmed for {{ e3 }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
