    lol:spellDescription "Passively grants Quinn Attack Speed and Move Speed after she attacks a Vulnerable target. Activate to have Valor reveal a large area nearby." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Passive: Attacking a Vulnerable target grants Quinn {{ attackspeedbonus*100 }}% Attack Speed and {{ e3 }}% Move Speed for {{ e1 }} seconds.Active: Valor reveals a large area nearby for {{ e5 }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
