    lol:spellSlot "R" ;
    lol:spellId "Tremors2" ;
    lol:spellName "Soaring Slam" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Rammus hops into the air and slams down at a target area, dealing magic damage and slowing enemies. If cast while Rammus is in Powerball, Rammus knocks up enemies near the center as well." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Rammus hops into the air and slams down in an area, dealing {{ initialdamagecalc }} magic damage and Slowing by {{ slowamount*100 }}% for {{ slowduration }} seconds. If used during Powerball, enemies in the center take an additional {{ spell.powerball:powerballdamage }} magic damage and are Knocked Up for {{ knockupduration }} seconds.Rammus then creates {{ numberofpulses }} aftershocks in the area over {{ buffduration }} seconds, repeating the Slow.The range of this Ability is increased by Rammus's Move Speed.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
