    lol:spellName "Queen's Wrath / Prey Seeker" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Rek'Sai's next 3 basic attacks deal bonus Physical Damage to nearby enemies.While Burrowed, Rek'Sai launches a burst of void-charged earth that damages and reveals enemies hit." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Unburrowed: Rek'Sai's next 3 Attacks within {{ buffduration }} seconds gain {{ attackspeed*100 }}% Attack Speed and deal an additional {{ totaldamagetooltip }} physical damage to nearby enemies. Attacks refresh the duration of this Ability.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
