    lol:spellDescription "Rek'Sai bites her target, dealing physical damage, or bonus true damage if she has max Fury.While Burrowed, Rek'Sai creates a re-usable, long lasting tunnel. Enemies can destroy it by standing on top of either entrance." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Unburrowed: Rek'Sai bites a target, dealing {{ spell.reksaie:basedamage }} physical damage. At max Fury, the bite deals {{ spell.reksaie:empowereddamage }} true damage instead.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
