    lol:spellDescription "Rek'Sai passively marks targets by damaging them. She can activate this ability to become briefly untargetable and lunge at a marked target for heavy damage based on their maximum health." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Rek'Sai targets an enemy damaged by her in the last {{ preymarkduration }} seconds and then dives underground, becoming Untargetable. Moments later, she leaps unstoppably at her target, dealing {{ rbasedamagecalc }} plus {{ percenthealthdamage }}% max Health physical damage and resets the cooldown of Burrow / Un-burrow.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
