    lol:spellDescription "Passive: Rell gains out of combat Move Speed.Active: Rell and an ally gain ramping Move Speed, doubled toward enemies and each other. Her next Attack explodes, dealing magic damage." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Rell and an ally charge, gaining {{ minms*100 }}% Move Speed, increased to {{ maxms*100 }}% when facing enemy champions or each other for {{ duration }} seconds. Rell's next Attack or Shattering Strike explodes in an area for {{ maxhealthdamagecalc }} max Health magic damage.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
