    lol:spellName "Junkyard Titan" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Every spell Rumble casts gives him Heat. When he reaches 50% Heat he reaches Danger Zone, granting all his basic abilities bonus effects. When he reaches 100% Heat, he starts Overheating, gaining bonus Attack Speed and granting his basic attacks bonus damage, but making him unable to cast spells for a few seconds." ;
    lol:belongsToChampion champ:Rumble .

