    lol:spellName "Wild Rush" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Samira dashes through an enemy (including structures), slashing enemies she passes through and gaining Attack Speed. Killing an enemy champion refreshes this ability's cooldown." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Samira dashes through an enemy (including structures), slashing enemies she passes through dealing {{ dashdamage }} magic damage and gaining {{ bonusattackspeed*100 }}% Attack Speed for {{ attackspeedduration }} seconds. If an enemy champion is killed within 3 seconds of Samira damaging them, This Ability's Cooldown is reset.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
