    lol:spellDescription "Samira unleashes a torrent of shots from her weapons, wildly shooting all enemies surrounding her." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Samira can only use this Ability if her current Style rating is S. Using this Ability consumes all Style rating.Samira unleashes a torrent of shots from her weapons, wildly shooting all enemies surrounding her 10 times over 2 seconds, each shot dealing {{ damagecalc }} physical damage and applying Life Steal at {{ lifestealmod*100 }}% effectiveness. Each shot can also critically strike.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
