    lol:spellDescription "Seraphine Shields and Hastes nearby allies. If she is already Shielded she will Heal nearby allies as well." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Seraphine spurs her nearby allied champions in song, granting them {{ hastevalueallies }} Move Speed, herself {{ wmsbonustotal }} decaying Move Speed and both {{ shieldvalueseraphine }} Shield for {{ shieldduration }} seconds.If Seraphine is already Shielded, she calls out to her allies to join her, restoring {{ wmissinghpheal }}% missing Health to them after a {{ whealsplitdelay }} second delay.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
