    lol:spellDescription "Seraphine deals damage and charms enemies hit, refreshing the range with every allied or enemy champion hit." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Seraphine takes the stage, projecting a captivating force that Charms for {{ rchannelduration }} seconds and deals {{ r1totaldamage }} magic damage.Any champions struck (including allies) become part of the performance, extending the range of this Ability. Allied champions gain maximum Notes.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
