    lol:spellDescription "Creates a magical barrier that blocks a single enemy ability cast on Sivir. She receives health and a burst of movement speed if a spell is blocked." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Sivir creates a magical barrier for {{ e1 }} seconds that blocks the next incoming enemy Ability. If an ability is blocked, Sivir restores {{ totalheal }} health and triggers Fleet of Foot.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
