    lol:spellName "On The Hunt" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Sivir leads her allies in battle, granting them a surge of Move Speed for a period of time. In addition, Sivir's attacks reduce her spell cooldowns." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Sivir rallies her nearby allies, granting them {{ maxms*100 }}% Move Speed for {{ ultduration }} seconds.Sivir's attacks against champions while On The Hunt reduce the cooldown of her basic abilities by 0.5 seconds.Takedowns on recently damaged enemies refreshes the duration of the hunt.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
