spell:Sona_Passive a lol:PassiveAbility, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:spellName "Power Chord" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Accelerando: Sona gains non-Ultimate ability haste permanently for her basic abilities as she uses her abilities well, up to a cap. Beyond that cap, further successful uses reduce her ultimate's remaining cooldown instead.Power Chord: Every few spell casts, Sona's next attack will deal bonus magic damage in addition to an additional effect based on what basic Ability Sona last activated." ;
    lol:belongsToChampion champ:Sona .

