    lol:spellTooltip "Syndra conjures a Dark Sphere, dealing {{ totaldamage }} magic damage. The Dark Sphere remains for {{ sphereduration }} seconds and can be manipulated by Syndra's other Abilities.{{ spell.syndrapassive:q1upgradethreshold }} Splinters of Wrath: Syndra can store {{ upgrade1maxammo }} charges of Dark Sphere.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
