champ:Taliyah a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Taliyah" ;
    lol:championKey "163" ;
    lol:championName "Taliyah" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Stoneweaver" ;
    lol:blurb "Taliyah is a nomadic mage from Shurima, torn between teenage wonder and adult responsibility. She has crossed nearly all of Valoran on a journey to learn the true nature of her growing powers, though more recently she has returned to protect her tribe..." ;
    lol:lore "Taliyah is a nomadic mage from Shurima, torn between teenage wonder and adult responsibility. She has crossed nearly all of Valoran on a journey to learn the true nature of her growing powers, though more recently she has returned to protect her tribe. Some have mistaken her compassion for weakness and paid the ultimate price—for beneath Taliyah's youthful demeanor is a will strong enough to move mountains, and a spirit fierce enough to make the earth itself tremble." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.05" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Try to throw enemies into Unraveled Earth using Seismic Shove." ;
    lol:allyTip "Remember, you don't always have to ride Weaver's Wall." ;
    lol:allyTip "Once you have Rylai's Crystal Scepter, casting Threaded Volley at enemies chasing you is a great way of making them regret everything." ;
    lol:enemyTip "When Taliyah casts Unraveled Earth in the lane, be on the lookout for Seismic Shove. If she throws you into her minefield, the throws and stones will break your bones." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Taliyah's Threaded Volley is locked into a direction. If she's throwing rocks at you, dodge to the side!" ;
