champ:Taric a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Taric" ;
    lol:championKey "44" ;
    lol:championName "Taric" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Shield of Valoran" ;
    lol:blurb "Taric is the Aspect of the Protector, wielding incredible power as Runeterra's guardian of life, love, and beauty. Shamed by a dereliction of duty and exiled from his homeland Demacia, Taric ascended Mount Targon to find redemption, only to discover a..." ;
    lol:lore "Taric is the Aspect of the Protector, wielding incredible power as Runeterra's guardian of life, love, and beauty. Shamed by a dereliction of duty and exiled from his homeland Demacia, Taric ascended Mount Targon to find redemption, only to discover a higher calling among the stars. Imbued with the might of ancient Targon, the Shield of Valoran now stands ever vigilant against the insidious corruption of the Void." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.15" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "The cooldown reducing component of Bravado makes Cooldown Reduction items like Frozen Heart, Iceborn Gauntlet, and Spirit Visage exceptionally powerful on Taric." ;
    lol:allyTip "Using Starlight's Touch at lower charges makes its healing less Mana efficient, but can greatly increase Taric's sustained damage via Bravado." ;
    lol:allyTip "Rather than saving Cosmic Radiance for the last moment and risking someone dying during the delay, it can be more beneficial to cast it as soon as you know a teamfight is guaranteed to start." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Taric's ultimate, Cosmic Radiance, has a long delay before its effect. Try to quickly assess whether to disengage the fight or attempt to kill his allies before it goes off." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Taric reduces his spell cooldowns by basic attacking enemies with Bravado. Try to kite him in teamfights and punish him for approaching the minion wave in lane." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Support ;
    lol:hasRole role:Tank ;
    lol:hasResourceType res:Mana ;
    lol:isFromRegion region:Targon ;
