champ:Thresh a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Thresh" ;
    lol:championKey "412" ;
    lol:championName "Thresh" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Chain Warden" ;
    lol:blurb "Sadistic and cunning, Thresh is an ambitious and restless specter of the Shadow Isles. Once the custodian of countless arcane secrets, he was undone by a power greater than life or death, and now sustains himself by tormenting and breaking others with..." ;
    lol:lore "Sadistic and cunning, Thresh is an ambitious and restless specter of the Shadow Isles. Once the custodian of countless arcane secrets, he was undone by a power greater than life or death, and now sustains himself by tormenting and breaking others with slow, excruciating inventiveness. His victims suffer far beyond their brief mortal coil as Thresh wreaks agony upon their souls, imprisoning them in his unholy lantern to torture for all eternity." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.18" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Communication is key when making use of Thresh's lantern. Let your teammates know how you like to use it." ;
    lol:allyTip "Death Sentence and Flay can be combined in either cast order for powerful combinations." ;
    lol:allyTip "Thresh can collect souls without needing to kill units himself. Planning your map position to be near the most deaths will help to maximize soul collection." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Thresh's Death Sentence has a long cast time. Watch for the cast to begin to take evasive actions." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Intentionally breaking a wall of The Box can allow a vulnerable ally to escape unscathed." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Thresh relies on collecting souls for a portion of his defense and damage. Try punishing him when he moves to collect them." ;
    lol:hasRole role:Support ;
    lol:hasRole role:Tank ;
    lol:hasResourceType res:Mana ;
    lol:isFromRegion region:Shadow_Isles ;
    lol:playsPosition pos:Support ;
