    lol:spellName "Rocket Jump" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Tristana fires at the ground to propel her to a distant location, dealing damage and slowing surrounding units for a brief period where she lands." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Tristana launches herself, dealing {{ landingdamage }} magic damage and Slowing by {{ slowmod*-100 }}% for {{ slowduration }} seconds upon landing.Champion takedowns and max stack Explosive Charge detonations on champions refresh this Ability's Cooldown.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
