champ:Trundle a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Trundle" ;
    lol:championKey "48" ;
    lol:championName "Trundle" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Troll King" ;
    lol:blurb "Trundle is a hulking and devious troll with a particularly vicious streak, and there is nothing he cannot bludgeon into submission—not even the Freljord itself. Fiercely territorial, he chases down anyone foolish enough to enter his domain. Then, his..." ;
    lol:lore "Trundle is a hulking and devious troll with a particularly vicious streak, and there is nothing he cannot bludgeon into submission—not even the Freljord itself. Fiercely territorial, he chases down anyone foolish enough to enter his domain. Then, his massive club of True Ice at the ready, he chills his enemies to the bone and impales them with jagged, frozen pillars, laughing as they bleed out onto the tundra." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.03" ;
    lol:costBE "1575"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "790"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Trundle excels at fighting within his Frozen Domain. Try to draw enemies onto it." ;
    lol:allyTip "Use Subjugate to soften a powerful enemy tank or to create a target for your team to focus fire." ;
    lol:allyTip "Chomp is good for lowering the physical damage of enemies; try to focus it on enemy physical damage dealers." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Trundle is very powerful at location-based combat. Try to draw him off of his Frozen Domain." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Make sure to get out of his Pillar of Ice as quickly as possible, as it significantly slows you down." ;
