    lol:spellTooltip "Twisted Fate begins shuffling his deck, allowing him to Recast to lock in one of three cards and enhance his next Attack.The Blue Card deals {{ bluedamage }} magic damage and restores {{ e6 }} Mana.The Red Card deals {{ reddamage }} to nearby enemies and Slows by {{ e2 }}% for 2.5 seconds.The Gold Card deals {{ golddamage }} and Stuns for {{ e3 }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
