    lol:spellTooltip "Twisted Fate focuses on his cards, granting True Sight of all enemy champions on the map for {{ e1 }} seconds and allowing him to Recast.Recast: Twisted Fate teleports up to {{ e4 }} units away.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
