    lol:spellDescription "Twitch hurls a cask of venom that explodes in an area, slowing targets and applying deadly venom to the target." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Twitch hurls a cask that adds a stack of Deadly Venom to all enemies struck and leaves behind a toxic cloud that persists for {{ duration }} seconds.Enemies that remain within the cloud are Slowed by {{ totalslowamount }}% and receive an additional stack of Deadly Venom each second.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
