    lol:spellDescription "Twitch unleashes the full power of his crossbow, shooting bolts over a great distance that pierce all enemies caught in their path." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Twitch unleashes his crossbow, gaining {{ bonusrange }} Attack Range and {{ bonusad }} Attack Damage, and causing his Attacks to become piercing bolts for {{ duration }} seconds. These bolts hit all enemies they pass through, but deal {{ falloffdamage*100 }}% less damage to subsequent targets, down to a minimum of {{ minimumfalloffdamage*100 }}% damage.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
