    lol:spellName "Final Hour" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Readying herself for an epic confrontation, Vayne gains increased Attack Damage, Invisibility during Tumble, reduced Tumble cooldown, and more bonus Move Speed from Night Hunter" ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Vayne gains {{ bonusattackdamage }} Attack Damage for {{ baseduration }} seconds, extended by {{ durationtoadd }} seconds whenever a champion damaged by Vayne dies within {{ damagedmarkerduration }} seconds. Additionally, during the duration:Night Hunter instead grants {{ movementspeed }} Move Speed.The Cooldown of Tumble is reduced by {{ tumblecdreduction }}%, and grants Invisibility for {{ tumblestealthduration }} second.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
