    lol:spellId "VelkozQ" ;
    lol:spellName "Plasma Fission" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Vel'Koz shoots a bolt of plasma that splits in two on reactivation or upon hitting an enemy. The bolt slows and damages on hit." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Vel'Koz shoots a plasma bolt that deals {{ totaldamage }} magic damage and Slows by {{ slowamount*100 }}% decaying over {{ slowduration }} second(s). At the end of its range, on hitting a target, or on Recasting, the bolt splits and fires two new bolts at a 90 degree angle.Killing a unit with this restores {{ tooltipmanarefund }} Mana.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
