    lol:spellDescription "Vi runs down an enemy, knocking aside anyone in the way. When she reaches her target she knocks it into the air, jumps after it, and slams it back into the ground." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Vi singles out an enemy champion, revealing them and dashing unstoppably towards them. Upon reaching them, Vi Knocks them Up for {{ rstunduration }} seconds and deals {{ damage }} physical damage.Any other enemies Vi collides with are dealt damage, knocked aside, and Stunned for {{ secondarytargetstunduration }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
