    lol:spellName "Frenzied Maul" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Volibear damages an enemy, applying on-hit effects and marking them.  Casting this ability again on the same target deals bonus damage and Heals Volibear." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Volibear mauls an enemy, dealing {{ totaldamage }} physical damage and marking them for {{ markduration }} seconds.If this Ability is used on a marked target, its damage is increased to {{ empowereddamage }} and Volibear restores {{ baseheal }} plus {{ percentmissinghealthhealingratio }} missing Health.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
