    lol:spellName "Stormbringer" ;
    lol:spellDescription "Volibear leaps to a target location, Slowing and damaging enemies beneath him while gaining bonus Health.  Enemy towers near his landing location become temporarily disabled." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Volibear transforms and leaps, gaining {{ healthamount }} Health and {{ bonusattackrange }} Attack Range for the next {{ transformduration }} seconds.Upon landing, Volibear cracks the earth, Disabling nearby towers for {{ towerdisableduration }} seconds and dealing {{ towerdamagetooltip }} physical damage to them. Nearby enemies are Slowed by {{ slowamount*100 }}%, decaying over 1 second. Enemies directly underneath Volibear suffer {{ sweetspotdamagetooltip }} physical damage.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
