champ:Warwick a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Warwick" ;
    lol:championKey "19" ;
    lol:championName "Warwick" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Uncaged Wrath of Zaun" ;
    lol:blurb "Warwick is a monster who hunts the gray alleys of Zaun. Transformed by agonizing experiments, his body is fused with an intricate system of chambers and pumps, machinery filling his veins with alchemical rage. He bursts from the shadows to prey upon..." ;
    lol:lore "Warwick is a monster who hunts the gray alleys of Zaun. Transformed by agonizing experiments, his body is fused with an intricate system of chambers and pumps, machinery filling his veins with alchemical rage. He bursts from the shadows to prey upon those criminals who terrorize the city's depths. Warwick is drawn to blood, driven mad by its scent… and none who spill it can escape him." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V25.20" ;
    lol:costBE "225"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "260"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Follow your Blood Hunt trails to low health enemy champions." ;
    lol:allyTip "Infinite Duress (R)'s distance scales with any Move Speed you gain, even from ally buffs and summoner spells." ;
    lol:allyTip "Jaws of the Beast (Q) will follow enemies who run, dash or teleport if you keep the button held down." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Warwick's attacks heal him at low health. Save your disables to finish him off." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Warwick is empowered versus low health enemies. Manage your health to keep him at bay." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Warwick's ultimate cast range scales with his Move Speed." ;
