    lol:championId "XinZhao" ;
    lol:championKey "5" ;
    lol:championName "Xin Zhao" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Seneschal of Demacia" ;
    lol:blurb "Xin Zhao is a resolute warrior loyal to the ruling Lightshield dynasty. Once condemned to the fighting pits of Noxus, he survived countless gladiatorial bouts, but after being freed by Demacian forces, he swore his life and allegiance to these brave..." ;
    lol:lore "Xin Zhao is a resolute warrior loyal to the ruling Lightshield dynasty. Once condemned to the fighting pits of Noxus, he survived countless gladiatorial bouts, but after being freed by Demacian forces, he swore his life and allegiance to these brave liberators. Armed with his favored three-talon spear, Xin Zhao now fights for his adopted kingdom, audaciously challenging any foe, no matter the odds." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Physical" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.03" ;
    lol:costBE "675"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "585"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Xin Zhao is a great initiator to combat. Lead the front to start a fight and use your ultimate to do the most damage possible." ;
    lol:allyTip "Try to position yourself so your ultimate's knockback is most effective." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Xin Zhao is a powerful initiator with both his charge and ultimate dealing damage to all units around him. Try having your team stay spread out until he's used his ultimate." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Xin Zhao relies heavily on his Three Talon Strikes for damage and cooldown resets, so preventing him from finishing his combo will have a dramatic effect." ;
