    lol:spellDescription "Xin Zhao slashes in front of himself with his spear, then thrusts it forward, slowing affected enemies and marking them as Challenged." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Xin Zhao slashes, dealing {{ slashdamage }} physical damage, then thrusts, dealing {{ thrustdamage }}. Enemies hit by the thrust are Slowed by {{ e6 }}% for {{ e7 }} seconds. Champions and Large Monsters hit by the thrust are marked as Challenged for {{ markduration }} seconds and revealed unless Stealthed.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
