    lol:spellDescription "Xin Zhao charges to an enemy, gaining increased Attack Speed and dealing damage to all enemies in the area, slowing them briefly. This Ability gains increased range against Challenged targets." ;
    lol:spellTooltip "Xin Zhao charges an enemy, dealing {{ chargedamage }} magic damage to nearby enemies and Slowing them by {{ baseslowamount }}% for {{ e6 }} seconds.Xin Zhao also grants himself {{ e3 }}% Attack Speed for {{ e4 }} seconds.This Ability's range is increased on enemies that are Challenged. {{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
