    lol:spellTooltip "Passive: Yunara deal {{ calc_passive_damage }} magic damage %i:OnHit% On-Hit and attacking grants {{ resource_nonchampion }} Unleash ({{ resource_champion }} Unleash for champions).Active: Yunara consumes {{ resource_max }} Unleash and for {{ buff_duration }} seconds gains {{ calc_attack_speed }} Attack Speed and deals an additional {{ calc_damage }} magic damage %i:OnHit% On-Hit. During this time, her Attacks spread to nearby enemies dealing them {{ calc_damage_spread }} physical damage.Transcendent State: This Ability is instantly activated for {{ spell.yunarar:buff_duration }} seconds.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}" ;
