champ:Zac a lol:Champion, owl:NamedIndividual ;
    lol:championId "Zac" ;
    lol:championKey "154" ;
    lol:championName "Zac" ;
    lol:championTitle "the Secret Weapon" ;
    lol:blurb "Zac is the product of a toxic spill that ran through a chemtech seam and pooled in an isolated cavern deep in Zaun's Sump. Despite such humble origins, Zac has grown from primordial ooze into a thinking being who dwells in the city's pipes, occasionally..." ;
    lol:lore "Zac is the product of a toxic spill that ran through a chemtech seam and pooled in an isolated cavern deep in Zaun's Sump. Despite such humble origins, Zac has grown from primordial ooze into a thinking being who dwells in the city's pipes, occasionally emerging to help those who cannot help themselves or to rebuild the broken infrastructure of Zaun." ;
    lol:adaptiveType "Magic" ;
    lol:lastChanged "V26.05" ;
    lol:costBE "2400"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:costRP "880"^^xsd:integer ;
    lol:allyTip "Picking up goo chunks is very important to staying alive." ;
    lol:allyTip "When Cell Division is ready, try to die in a position that makes it difficult for the enemy team to kill your bloblets." ;
    lol:allyTip "Charging Elastic Slingshot from the fog of war will give opponents less time to react." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Zac heals from the goo that separates from him. You can crush the goo pieces by stepping on them." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Kill all of Zac's bloblets when he splits apart to stop him from reforming." ;
    lol:enemyTip "Silences, stuns, roots and knockups will all interrupt Zac when he is charging Elastic Slingshot." ;
